I prayed over this a lot last night because of all the people saying, "Hey, they didn't notify me.

00:00:11.370 --> 00:00:17.072
" It bothered me because so many of you would like to be here and YouTube was not telling you.

00:00:23.164 --> 00:00:31.440
We came to the conclusion that because we uploaded three videos yesterday, it notified you every single time.

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:40.640
I think there's a limit to how many times you can do that so that people can actually be notified.

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.559
Am I saying that right?

00:00:42.559 --> 00:00:42.993
Yeah.

00:00:43.862 --> 00:00:54.640
We believe that now we're seeing how many people will get notified to come pray with us versus having three uploads.

00:01:10.343 --> 00:01:10.640
It was too much.

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:14.180
So, we're just going to do this.

00:01:14.180 --> 00:01:31.176
Another thing we found out is that Braden can post on X that we're doing a live, and everybody comes over from X because it notifies you immediately through Elon's.

00:01:42.120 --> 00:01:42.613
I thought that was pretty cool.

00:01:42.613 --> 00:01:51.142
I thought, "Okay, good thinking," because the more the merrier, you know.

00:01:51.142 --> 00:01:55.290
Good evening family; good morning, good afternoon wherever you are.

00:01:55.290 --> 00:02:04.267
It's awesome because so many of you from all over the world come and pray with us on a daily basis.

00:02:04.267 --> 00:02:12.360
One person said, "Hey, it's 7:00 in the morning," and I said, "Wow, that's just awesome.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:14.440
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:25.680
" We're going to go over everything the Lord showed us last night in prayer.

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:33.940
For those of you who didn't want to watch the beginning, I'll recap what the Lord said yesterday.

00:02:54.420 --> 00:03:00.230
I was in the shower praying and I sat there, just waiting before the Lord.

00:03:00.230 --> 00:03:19.580
He said, "What they don't realize is what you gave them at the beginning of yesterday's video is the key to everything in your Christian walk.

00:03:19.580 --> 00:03:28.811
" He said that will be what will sustain them in ministry and in their walk with Me.

00:03:34.514 --> 00:03:37.120
He said, "Brandon, everyone has a trigger.

00:03:37.554 --> 00:03:39.725
What sets you off?

00:03:39.725 --> 00:03:46.931
What's your boundary when it comes to certain conversations?

00:03:46.931 --> 00:03:50.647
What irritates you the most?

00:03:50.647 --> 00:03:54.587
What's your trigger?

00:03:54.587 --> 00:03:58.143
" I asked, "Your trigger?

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.209
" He said, "Do you know what My trigger is?

00:04:18.539 --> 00:04:19.029
" I said, "No, Lord.

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:32.960
" He said, "Touching the glory.

00:04:37.394 --> 00:04:37.989
" He said, "I'll show you scriptures.

00:04:37.989 --> 00:04:45.698
" Jesus says, "I do nothing unless I see My Father.

00:04:45.698 --> 00:04:49.260
Unless I'm instructed by My Father, I do nothing.

00:04:49.260 --> 00:04:53.920
" Everything He did was to give God praise and glory.

00:04:56.300 --> 00:04:57.859
"I do nothing apart from the Lord.

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:13.573
Everything that I do in word and in deed, we give all the glory to God.

00:05:13.573 --> 00:05:23.910
" He said, "My trigger, Brandon, what bothers Me the most is touching the glory.

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:29.500
I will share My glory with no one.

00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:33.489
" I was taken up and I saw Lucifer.

00:05:33.489 --> 00:05:36.219
He was made for worship.

00:05:36.219 --> 00:05:43.140
Everything about him was glorious as he walked around in heaven leading worship and music.

00:05:45.420 --> 00:05:49.713
The angels would say, "Oh, you did a good job.

00:05:51.771 --> 00:05:53.940
The worship was just beautiful today.

00:06:03.279 --> 00:06:08.880
" In that praise and acknowledgment, I could see that giving him glory lifted his ego and his pride, taking the glory from the Father.

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:11.863
He said, "I will exalt myself.

00:06:11.863 --> 00:06:13.700
I will do all this.

00:06:13.700 --> 00:06:16.150
" Suddenly, he was shot down like lightning.

00:06:16.150 --> 00:06:18.960
He touched the glory.

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:22.389
He took the praise.

00:06:28.635 --> 00:06:36.777
The moment he had an ego and started to think, "I'll exalt myself above God.

00:06:36.777 --> 00:06:38.640
I'll be bigger.

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:44.400
I'll put my kingdom above His because don't you realize who I am?

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:56.186
" he didn't realize the presence was coming from the Father through him to give the Father worship.

00:06:58.860 --> 00:06:59.856
The moment he thought he was something, it changed.

00:06:59.856 --> 00:07:09.348
Everything we do in ministry, everything we say, everything we impart is not us.

00:07:09.348 --> 00:07:17.520
Me seeing things is not me; it's all to His glory.

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:21.880
That's why I said we're the glove.

00:07:21.880 --> 00:07:25.288
We have this glove that's like a snow glove.

00:07:25.288 --> 00:07:34.839
It's a really cool thing, but it was made to give warmth to the hand.

00:07:38.659 --> 00:07:49.720
The moment the Holy Spirit goes inside of that glove, the human body, it brings life to the glove.

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:54.747
But the glove is nothing without the Holy Spirit.

00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:17.790
A human hand goes in there, and the glove is nothing without the hand.

00:08:17.790 --> 00:08:29.120
That's why the Lord was showing me, "Brandon, I'll share My glory with no one in the days ahead.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.960
" Even more so with what you're about to see.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:48.399
"If you want longevity in ministry, son, and you want to know My trigger: touch not the glory through the praise of man.

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:50.344
" People say, "Oh, you're so good.

00:08:50.344 --> 00:08:52.500
You're awesome.

00:08:52.500 --> 00:08:57.280
" But people's opinions change like the water, the weather, and the tide.

00:08:57.280 --> 00:09:00.263
It always goes back and forth.

00:09:00.263 --> 00:09:13.920
He said people's opinions of you will always change—how great they say you are or how great they don't.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:25.770
The comment section, the peanut gallery.

00:09:25.770 --> 00:09:32.769
He was talking to me about finding your box.

00:09:32.769 --> 00:09:34.990
What is your box?

00:09:40.856 --> 00:09:42.000
Like William Seymour, who took his flesh and told it to shut up.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:47.760
As I told you all yesterday, what's your box?

00:09:47.760 --> 00:10:08.640
William Seymour sat in the front of the stage with a box on his head for sometimes 45 minutes to an hour before the service would even start as a display of humility so that He gets the glory.

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:19.440
Regardless of what happens in this vast auditorium, He gets the glory, the honor, and the praise.

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:22.205
"I'll share My glory with no one.

00:10:34.460 --> 00:10:36.880
" In the days ahead, you'll see this more and more.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:46.959
He said, "As long, Brandon, as you decrease so that I increase, we'll get along just fine.

00:10:46.959 --> 00:10:54.239
" Basically, He wants to use people in a great capacity, but everyone has a trigger.

00:10:54.239 --> 00:10:56.439
What's your trigger?

00:10:56.439 --> 00:11:08.000
When you get to know the Father more intimately, you realize there are boundaries with His triggers—what He loves and what He doesn't.

00:11:11.748 --> 00:11:13.760
So I sit before Him and listen as He talks to me about what's coming.

00:11:18.229 --> 00:11:24.240
He tells me about finances, the president, what's coming after the attack with Venezuela, what's happening next for China, and what's coming for Taiwan.

00:11:25.773 --> 00:11:34.427
You learn these things as you sit at His feet and die to yourself.

00:11:34.427 --> 00:11:36.969
That's why you die daily.

00:11:46.549 --> 00:11:46.846
What are you dying to?

00:11:46.846 --> 00:11:47.440
Self.

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:57.622
When the anointing's on me and the cloak comes on, I'm just that glove.

00:12:00.171 --> 00:12:04.999
The moment it moves out after the livestream's over, I'm just as helpless as anyone.

00:12:04.999 --> 00:12:11.896
When that anointing is on, you feel like Superman and the glory is there.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:27.703
But the Lord said impartations, healings, and manifestations like you wouldn't believe are about to come to this planet.

00:12:43.250 --> 00:12:43.480
We're about to see things we've always dreamed of seeing.

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:52.195
He said, "There's a difference between being a general in an army and being one of the foot soldiers.

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:09.920
" You can be a general in His army for what's coming, though all of us are important and have a position.

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:17.955
The foot soldiers are just as important as the generals, but the general has a lot more responsibility.

00:13:17.955 --> 00:13:23.031
To whom much is given, much is required.

00:13:23.031 --> 00:13:40.023
General Flynn and all the generals we've had in our military had a lot more responsibility, and if they messed up, it cost a lot of lives.

00:13:40.023 --> 00:13:55.342
So, they have to be on target and precise with what they are hearing from the commander-in-chief of the United States of America, our president, right?

00:13:58.070 --> 00:14:04.571
You distribute the message to the people and they help bring out the call and we win battles.

00:14:08.120 --> 00:14:15.988
The Lord said, Brandon, there is a lot of difference between generals and privates and lieutenants and all that.

00:14:15.988 --> 00:14:30.640
It is interesting, so you learn the chain of command and you learn a lot of things as I grow, and he instructs me all the time.

00:14:52.269 --> 00:14:52.545
This is what you are going to do and this is what you are not going to do, and I want you to do it precisely.

00:14:52.545 --> 00:14:53.375
Yes, sir.

00:15:00.914 --> 00:15:02.740
So, as I sat before him today, he said, I want you to tell my people again, humble themselves underneath the mighty hand of God.

00:15:02.740 --> 00:15:03.840
Humble yourself.

00:15:03.840 --> 00:15:16.269
No matter what your potter's wheel experience is, no matter what you are going through, you do not have to announce it on Facebook.

00:15:16.269 --> 00:15:21.430
You do not have to tell everybody your business.

00:15:30.056 --> 00:15:30.320
You know, I am on the potter's wheel right now and everything is so rough.

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:41.199
You know how many times I went on Facebook and told everybody about me?

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:54.399
I never once told anybody how bad my day was, other than my grandmother across the street, of how rough some days were.

00:15:56.018 --> 00:15:58.579
I did not even tell my mom and my dad.

00:15:58.579 --> 00:16:03.893
Nobody knew other than her because she lived across the street.

00:16:20.248 --> 00:16:20.551
But I did not make an announcement on Facebook so everybody would pray for me.

00:16:28.980 --> 00:16:31.500
I did not tell every sister so and so how much I was going through because I wanted them to feel sorry for me and give me finances.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:36.373
Do not give ministry of hints.

00:16:36.373 --> 00:16:44.107
Well, you know, we are having a hard time financially.

00:16:59.715 --> 00:16:59.964
I have got ten dollars left, five dollars left.

00:16:59.964 --> 00:17:10.687
I did not make the announcement so that people would still feel sorry for me.

00:17:25.199 --> 00:17:30.060
I thought if God can provide and God knows how much I need, I do not need sister so and so or brother so and so to try to meet that need.

00:17:30.060 --> 00:17:34.639
Either God does it or he is not God.

00:17:51.547 --> 00:17:51.853
But ministry of hints is not God.

00:17:51.853 --> 00:17:55.679
Well, you know, won't you help me?

00:17:55.679 --> 00:18:01.016
I have got my bills going to be cut off this next week.

00:18:01.016 --> 00:18:06.834
Ministry of hints is not God.

00:18:06.834 --> 00:18:27.211
Keep your mouth shut, and if you have sowed and you have tithed and you have given, keep your eyes on him, not on man.

00:18:40.916 --> 00:18:41.120
The moment man becomes your provider you are in trouble.

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:49.931
The moment man becomes your need maker, the way maker, you are in trouble.

00:18:52.080 --> 00:19:00.080
I do not need a miracle behind my mailbox.

00:19:00.080 --> 00:19:01.480
I need Jesus.

00:19:09.439 --> 00:19:12.480
That is why Diana's dream, when she had the dream, the lady was looking at her and the glory was on us and she said, Oh, don't you see?

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:13.980
It is just Jesus.

00:19:13.980 --> 00:19:22.853
When people see you in the days ahead and your face is shining with glory, it is not about you.

00:19:23.520 --> 00:19:28.380
The world is going to be attracted to it and the blessings flow through it.

00:19:28.380 --> 00:19:30.180
Increase comes from it.

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:32.799
But that is not the focus.

00:19:58.542 --> 00:19:58.826
The focus is Jesus.

00:19:59.110 --> 00:20:06.331
And the glory will be on you, ladies and gentlemen, for what I have seen.

00:20:06.331 --> 00:20:11.831
A level of the glory that we have never seen before.

00:20:11.831 --> 00:20:33.200
And when we go into the Walmarts and the Targets and the Sam's or Costco or wherever you go shopping and they see that glory on you, it is just Jesus.

00:20:45.627 --> 00:20:45.840
You always deflect to him.

00:20:46.907 --> 00:20:47.120
You must know this.

00:20:47.120 --> 00:20:58.519
I told Braden and Diana and Paisley today, I said, this is God's trigger.

00:20:58.519 --> 00:21:00.679
This is so important.

00:21:04.794 --> 00:21:15.589
And to the point that I am turning off the comment section.

00:21:35.498 --> 00:21:36.310
It is not about Brandon.

00:21:36.320 --> 00:22:04.133
This is not about how great Brandon is or how much he hears or what he does not hear and the egg throwers or the praise or the palm leaf people.

00:22:04.133 --> 00:22:18.853
This is just me being obedient to what God has called me to do and what he has called me to say.

00:22:39.120 --> 00:22:39.440
And if I miss it, I miss it.

00:22:40.537 --> 00:22:41.873
And that is between me and him.

00:22:41.873 --> 00:22:57.840
Or if it is right and I pray it is, you know, I do not want to cause any prophetic confusion, but it is always to give glory to him.

00:22:57.840 --> 00:23:00.960
Die to yourself.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:02.290
Die to yourself.

00:23:02.290 --> 00:23:04.192
I saw it today.

00:23:04.192 --> 00:23:15.280
I have heard people say it a thousand times and I thought what are they truly saying until it became Rhema to me.

00:23:37.577 --> 00:23:37.840
You can parrot things so much and I hear somebody, I heard a parrot one time.

00:23:37.840 --> 00:23:54.457
Oh Lord we give you all the glory and honor and praise, but yet they display something so much haughtiness upon them on the platform.

00:23:59.840 --> 00:24:26.290
So much pride, so much pride, and you see it and it is so much about attracting the glory to them as they move in the gift but yet you see the gift and you say, is it right?

00:24:26.290 --> 00:24:28.320
Are you right right now?

00:24:28.320 --> 00:24:32.009
No, it is so much about you.

00:24:32.009 --> 00:24:47.597
But when I see Katherine, she was always back, she did that thing and the Lord said, learn, I will share my glory with no one.

00:24:48.396 --> 00:24:59.856
You see, there is a lot of parrots that know how to parrot and copy what you have seen on the stage.

00:24:59.856 --> 00:25:11.074
There is a lot of parrots versus the ones that are really truly sold out and they are dead to it.

00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:28.116
And the Lord said, I am going to pour out my spirit on another level on people.

00:25:37.039 --> 00:25:37.359
Brandon, you are about to see some glorious things, but touch not the anointing.

00:25:37.359 --> 00:25:41.200
Don't ever take it and ever be arrogant.

00:25:41.200 --> 00:25:53.030
Humble yourself before me and I will flow through you and we will get along just fine.

00:25:53.030 --> 00:25:56.720
I say all this stuff to you to try to help you.

00:25:56.720 --> 00:26:00.811
Maybe it does, maybe it doesn't.

00:26:07.399 --> 00:26:07.659
It is like the comments.

00:26:07.659 --> 00:26:10.148
I say answered questions.

00:26:10.148 --> 00:26:14.767
He said, Who are you to answer any questions?

00:26:14.767 --> 00:26:19.919
Did I tell you to answer questions?

00:26:33.840 --> 00:26:34.053
It is not your gift.

00:26:34.053 --> 00:26:40.533
It is a Ferrari whenever it comes on.

00:26:58.960 --> 00:26:59.307
And everybody loves the Ferrari, but you are just the kid that is driving the borrowed Ferrari.

00:27:07.400 --> 00:27:07.740
It is not yours.

00:27:07.740 --> 00:27:12.272
It is daddy's Ferrari.

00:27:12.272 --> 00:27:20.430
But you are excited about the Ferrari and you are showing everybody and you are taking Instagram photos and look at me.

00:27:20.430 --> 00:27:28.515
Cool car, and the Lord said, That ain't your Ferrari, son.

00:27:29.599 --> 00:27:36.736
You are borrowing the keys for the moment.

00:28:01.840 --> 00:28:02.160
That ain't your car.

00:28:06.464 --> 00:28:07.232
You are a pretender.

00:28:26.259 --> 00:28:26.549
You have no business answering questions.

00:28:33.719 --> 00:28:34.159
It is not your gift.

00:28:34.159 --> 00:28:37.066
You are borrowing it for that time.

00:28:37.066 --> 00:28:38.559
Don't ever do that again.

00:28:56.080 --> 00:29:00.060
I said I will bow my head before you.

00:29:00.060 --> 00:29:02.159
Father, I am sorry.

00:29:02.159 --> 00:29:18.880
What do you ever think that you have the ability to answer anybody's question on there unless I tell you to say something?

00:29:19.084 --> 00:29:20.107
I, that is haughtiness.

00:29:20.107 --> 00:29:21.616
Don't ever do that again.

00:29:22.288 --> 00:29:26.060
I said I had no argument.

00:29:39.759 --> 00:29:40.399
It is a hard thing.

00:29:42.982 --> 00:30:47.900
It is like a stomach punch whenever I come before you and I just humble.

00:30:55.058 --> 00:30:57.840
I just like, and I am not wanting sister clipboard to come and say Brandon, you said this, you said that.

00:31:19.333 --> 00:31:19.787
You point out your own flaws.

00:31:24.075 --> 00:31:30.373
You look at your own stuff.

00:31:30.373 --> 00:31:35.360
Examine your own self.

00:31:45.726 --> 00:31:46.103
I am very public about how I am examined by the father looking at me through a microscope.

00:32:04.053 --> 00:32:04.600
He looks at me and he examines me all the time.

00:32:22.622 --> 00:32:22.827
What I am trying to tell you is that God is going to do something huge in these last days and he is not going to share his glory with no one.

00:32:27.220 --> 00:32:27.600
And he wants to do something huge through you.

00:32:27.600 --> 00:32:37.360
Examine yourself, humble yourself, and allow him to be big inside of you.

00:32:37.360 --> 00:32:43.893
Does that make sense what I am saying?

00:32:43.893 --> 00:33:12.053
When you lay hands on the sick and you see their eyes come back in their head and their arms grow out before you and you see hair grow back that was not there.

00:33:12.053 --> 00:33:27.440
When you see the dead raised in front of you and the media wants to put you all over the news, remember that you are the glove.

00:33:27.440 --> 00:33:32.479
Apart from him, you can do nothing.

00:33:32.479 --> 00:33:36.587
You did not do nothing.

00:33:36.587 --> 00:33:42.000
You are just the glove.

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:47.386
You will see the dead raised in the days ahead.

00:33:47.386 --> 00:33:55.200
You are going to see the blind eyes open.

00:33:55.200 --> 00:34:01.420
You are going to see ears open.

00:34:01.420 --> 00:34:22.450
You are going to see things that there is going to be shock and awe on Instagram, Facebook, the dead were raised.

00:34:22.450 --> 00:34:28.631
Did you see who did it?

00:34:28.631 --> 00:34:35.589
No, you did not do nothing.

00:34:35.599 --> 00:34:38.240
You were just the glove.

00:34:51.1000 --> 00:34:52.346
So, I am trying to prepare you for what is about to come.

00:34:52.346 --> 00:35:01.099
Take not the glory for what is about to come, ladies and gentlemen.

00:35:03.680 --> 00:35:03.822
I am just a vessel.

00:35:03.822 --> 00:35:05.240
We give him all the glory.

00:35:05.240 --> 00:35:08.320
Thank you for what you did today, Lord.

00:35:08.320 --> 00:35:08.992
Thank you.

00:35:30.693 --> 00:35:31.146
To you be all the glory.

00:35:42.697 --> 00:35:43.211
To you be all the honor.

00:35:49.168 --> 00:35:49.824
To you be all the praise.

00:35:49.824 --> 00:36:00.160
For the love that you had for your people today was bigger than Brandon could ever think about.

00:36:00.160 --> 00:36:02.120
It was his love.

00:36:19.170 --> 00:36:19.620
It was a display of his grace—something you don't earn and something you don't deserve.

00:36:26.800 --> 00:36:29.079
That's what we're about to see: a display of glorious grace, that by his stripes you are healed.

00:36:29.079 --> 00:36:32.232
By his stripes we are healed.

00:36:40.900 --> 00:36:41.170
It wasn't about how good we are or what we deserve; it was his grace.

00:36:42.949 --> 00:36:48.267
The provision that's about to happen for some of you—'I got a million dollars.

00:36:48.267 --> 00:36:54.240
' Be humble with what he's about to give you.

00:36:54.240 --> 00:37:01.576
Know it's for the kingdom, your bank accounts.

00:37:01.576 --> 00:37:11.312
He said, 'In a moment, in a 24-hour period, I'll make decamillionaires.

00:37:11.312 --> 00:37:22.840
' I'm going to speak to you in the middle of the night, Brandon, and you'll invest here, and then within a 24-hour period, it'll make you a million bucks.

00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:27.660
Brandon, listen to me: be humble with what I give you when I say to give it.

